Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lots of unusual items wash up onto the seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nuts from distant southern lands and seashells,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}giant deep-sea fish, and on rare occasions... people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And empty boats with no one on them as well...
