Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.69,0:02:20.66,EP Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2500,1000)\be1}Where Sea Meets Man
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:43.47,Alt,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard there's ferry from here to across the bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At this hour, I think everyone's out fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I guess I just have to wait till the afternoon then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing... in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife and I parted strangely out there on that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably don't want to hear the story, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually I do want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You do? Then let me tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was about two and a half years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This place reeks of fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined... your hometown was so rustic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Where do suggest we go back to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't have fired you for such a small mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The store was already about to go out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He was looking for a good excuse to get rid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did it have to be you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Father said he'd let you take over the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I got engaged with you, my peers became intensely envious of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They might have told your father stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:05:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And he probably never expected you \Nto follow me to these boonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I didn't think you would, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the eldest daughter,\Nand you must've had plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to go back, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This place isn't for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Missus, aren't you getting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Michihi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll apologize when we make land...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sea snakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's suddenly gotten hazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. The land's very visible. We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That way is the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it... I can't steer the rudder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon the boat! Swim this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Michihi! You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No... there are snakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Wh-where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that! Swim this way. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where... Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Michihi! {\alpha&HFF&}Michihi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Michihi! Michihi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow her boat. Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,502)}My boat capsized...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I washed ashore to this beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But no trace of my wife's boat was ever found.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because of the currents along this shore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,everything in the sea washes ashore here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If my wife's boat capsized as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,at least part of the cargo should wash up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Assuming she floated out to sea, \Nshe's probably dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But because I don't have any proof,\N I can't move from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Snakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've stayed here for two and a half years?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you find any evidence or not, \Nshe's no longer alive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she was rescued, she's living a new life now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:08:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time for you to think about your own life?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it was none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Haze...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Snakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, here's the usual amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to sell that in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you're paying her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You think because she doesn't know\N the going price in town...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too big a cut to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can charge twice that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk as if you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked a long time for a wholesaler...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of middlemen like you that the fishermen around here are poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even figuring in a fee for coming from town, \Nthis is what the price should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. At that price, I'll just go to the next village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, how about this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, but that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't go any lower than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can charge this much from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? Can I really charge this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the others, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I thought you were a strange person...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to sell for a good price today again... Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't much, but I want you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you check out of the inn \Nand come live next to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Make this place your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be great. Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes...\N- I think it's a good idea, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shark! There's a shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Shiro, don't scare us like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Was yesterday spring tide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's going on... the tide is awfully high.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a guy around here who was waiting for his wife for a long...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he gone now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That person is... living with us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So leave him alone, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but I'm afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been saying strange things lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And the tide has been rising without stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing but strange things have been happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You still stare out to sea for a while sometimes, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I worry you'll be washed out to sea with the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This rise in the tides is just like it was back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years or so ago, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... There was a haze just like this that time, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be better if we don't go out \Nfishing until this settles down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They say some boats that go out \Nin this haze don't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:13:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then about three years later,\N the boats return, empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The boats return, {\alpha&FF&}empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The boats return, empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it did come back, it wouldn't make it to shore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It still {\i1}does{\i0} bother you, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your story weighed on my mind, \Nso I did a lot of checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,According to what I learned, the boat would show up again soon, so I came back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That mass of snakes you saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No one else could see them. Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They were most likely mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard of {\i1}umisen-yamasen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40\bord2.5\fad(50,50)\pos(640,30.667)\i1}Note:- umi = sea, sen = 1000, yama = mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A snake that lives 1000 years in the sea and 1000 years in the mountains becomes a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This mushi has something in common with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, there's no way to tell \Nhow long they've actually lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,One is that amass and travel to the open sea while giving off something akin to haze...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...and another one is that live \Nquietly deep in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1689)}At a glance, both look no different from snakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes, the mountain mushi descend from the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sea mushi approach seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They gather at a single spot on the shore,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1766)}and a thousand days later, \Nthey merge into a single Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So the same thing I saw is back again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see anything from outside that haze,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but oddly, you can see out of it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've wondered
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,why only your wife was swallowed \Nby the haze back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,From inside the haze,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,only those who {\i1}want{\i0} to return to land\N can see the land and return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I saw you, it seemed you might \Nlose your desire to go on living
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,even if you found any of your wife's personal effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as you're aware of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you're welcome to come along on my sightseeing trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready for the worst?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost uncanny how well I can \Nsee land from inside this haze.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still see it, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Their numbers are huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is... that boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like her body is still in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull up alongside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Michihi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd all most given up hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving me here for days...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been at least three days, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What... in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I said some terrible things to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they were terrible things you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all right. You came to rescue me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I complained too much, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't mean it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see your hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's go there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now come on over to this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you still see land?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I can still see it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The land you should return to is... this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no longer human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The mushi have begun to transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't safe to remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back from that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Found them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We may never find them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, a giant wave's coming! Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the haze is clearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time we washed up on shore,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the villagers had long given up hope for our survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought we were out at sea \Nfor only two or three hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But on land, more than a month had passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside that haze, time was probably \Nrunning on mushi time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We could at least take some comfort in that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,she only had to spend three lonely days out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The following day, his wife's boat washed up on shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:22:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! What a fine kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Its owner is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.55,0:22:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's lovely...
